title: Quirkymals
description: Welcome to Quirkymals! With this multiplayer mash-up of aspects from your all-time favorite childhood games, you can personalize your favorite animal, hang out in countless fun locations, unravel mysteries, and compete with friends. Experience dozens of unique and challenging mini-games to earn coins for skins and other collectibles!

title: Social App
description: Social App was created using MongoDB, ExpressJS, ReactJS, NodeJS & Graphql aka (MERNG) Stack and has the simple features of singing up, singing in, and making a post. This project was made to get comfortable user-authentication, post request and other methods using a different tech stack.
